“Extend your life and don't stay here!”


Reviewed May 13, 2017




I have over 25 years on the road and this was the worst hotel place I have ever stayed at. The paint was coming off the wall in spots, the room was filthy, and the furniture has seen better days. That is not to mention the train that zipped by my room until 9:45 PM and started again very early in the morning. The hotel is only 100 feet or so from the tracks. The hallways stunk and I mean they were bad. The bed was like a rock and the linens did not look like they were clean. I will never stay at this place again.


Room Tip: Save your money and go somewhere else.
