Hotel Operations
                        We pride ourselves in providing our guests with clean, fresh and comfortable experiences that make their travels more enjoyable. From housekeepers and guest service representatives to maintenance engineers and night laundry associates, each team member plays an important role in our guest’s experience. Click here to find current openings.
                    






Hotel Management
                        Leading our frontline teams in our daily pursuit of providing comfortable, enjoyable and memorable stays for our guests is the responsibility of our Hotel Management.  These roles include: District Managers, Multi-Unit/Single Property General Managers, Assistant General Managers and Team Leads.  Click here to find current openings.
                    






Corporate 
                        Our Charlotte-based Corporate Support Center is the hub of Extended Stay America’s organization. The corporate office houses positions within the following areas: Facilities, Finance, Human Resources, IT, Legal, Marketing, Operations, Procurement, Revenue Management, and Sales. Click here to find current openings.
                    






Intern 
                        Start your career journey with Extended Stay America. Part of an internship at Extended Stay America is learning from leading industry professionals who will help you understand what it takes to make it in the hospitality space. Click here to find current openings.
                    




