jameslL278OS



Grand Haven, Michigan






1 review 





“Not a hotel it's for workers”


Reviewed 3 weeks ago




They tell you nothing and only clean the room after 6 days. Not a place for a family. The breakfast is a granola bar but the coffee is okay. You have to read their minds and ask for everything. We don't recommend it.





Stayed June 2017, traveled with family



