“Everything was Excellent”


Reviewed June 17, 2017




This hotel is very near to Cisco Systems(Approx 1.5 Miles), it's a pleasent stay and rooms were good, neat and comfortable. The management was awesome and helpful in all the aspects.The service, housekeeping and everything was simply good....I Stayed like 57 nights and i never felt any discomfort.





Stayed June 2017, traveled on business



