suites and amenities





view photos  view floor plans




        photo gallery










































Actual layout and features may vary.





        floor plan










































Actual layout and features may vary.



If you’re traveling for business or for fun and want a room that serves your many needs at an affordable price, Extended Stay America is your best choice. We’re hardly your ordinary hotel. Each of our clean, comfortable suites includes lots of room to relax, and many extras that make traveling easy. Whether you stay for a night, a week, or longer, you’ll enjoy the convenience of our spacious suites, always available at low nightly rates with discounts for extended stays.




free grab-and-go breakfast
Jumpstart your day with a free grab-and-go breakfast that includes a variety of breakfast bars and muffins, hot cereal, coffee, and tea.





fully equipped kitchens
Cook what you want when you want in your own kitchen, complete with stove, microwave, and refrigerator.





flat screen tv
Relax with your favorite shows—our new flat-screen TVs offer premium channels for free.





hot tub
Soak away the cares of travel in a relaxing hot tub (at select hotels).





shuttle
Take a convenient shuttle to local stores and restaurants (at select hotels).





filtered water
Fresh filtered water means one fewer worry and cost when on the road (at select hotels).





laundry
An on-site guest laundry at every hotel makes traveling easy.





pet-friendly rooms
You don't have to leave your four-legged friends at home, as we offer pet-friendly rooms in all our hotels. Learn more.





pool
Refresh and relax by a beautiful pool (at select hotels).





meeting room
Conducting business while away is easy in our accommodating meeting rooms (at select hotels).





airport shuttle
Our free airport shuttle takes the hassle out of getting to your flight (at select hotels).





fitness room
Maintain your exercise program while on the road by taking advantage of our fitness centers (at select hotels).





free Wi-Fi
At Extended Stay America, in-room Wi-Fi is a standard-- not a luxury. Enjoy free Wi-Fi at each of 629 locations nationwide.





 










